Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.92,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I float lightly in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:45.89,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}becoming one with...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.72,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}...the distant, glittering sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:52.64,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I read the wind, and wander away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:57.86,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}To a far off destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:01.36,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.66,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I fill my lungs and set off,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.03,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Taking in the world's spring breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:13.29,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}While at the sun above, everyone's smiles are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:16.25,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}In between our hellos and goodbyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:20.13,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}There is only us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:23.76,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}We can accomplish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:27.05,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The rays of the sun pass through,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.89,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Creating a newborn sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:35.65,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The promised morning arch that we were waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.69,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}As you wave to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:43.49,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I decide to share with you a special day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:47.07,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}And our idle chatter begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-chan is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you haven't forgotten anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I did text{"mail"? -Pipelynx} you yesterday after dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get any texts from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to put the other one on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well go barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-R-R{\fscx200}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run-chan?{Doki rules, one stutter}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-P{f\s0}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's me, how did I not notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I not notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kneel down! It'll be visible from the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it because I was sleepy? For such a petty reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.29,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Everybody forgets things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually not their panties, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru. Just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, you thought, "but not their panties," right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan! Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, huh? You sure have it tough, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm just not a morning person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm sleepy, I tend to space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the notes from yesterday's afternoon classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I copy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Now that you mention it, didn't you leave early yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you can. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot. You're a life saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What language is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got drowsy during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not just the mornings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a bit messy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me if you can't read something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a look afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind. Once you're done, pass it on to Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, are you nearsighted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How bad is your vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 20/20. These glasses are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing fake glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I don't wear these...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I see things I'd be better off not seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... not talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Yuuko, behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm only kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:28.43,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are really fun to tease!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I am nearsighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I can't deal with scary stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good actress, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be in the theatre club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm playing a ghost, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This summer, I have received two or three letters from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In them, you wrote, "I want to gather a considerable amount of knowledge in Tokyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Best regards."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.05,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I want to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to go to the toilet," would be way too embarrassing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, that's your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I'd like to go to the toilet, may I take Yuuko-chan to the infirmary on the way there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Run. You saved me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I had to go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also going to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Run, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but I feel nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I caught something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we go to the toilet? Or the infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, toilet... toilet... to... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan. That's not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:37.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs54\b1\pos(841.5,421.5)\frx6\fry16\frz349.267\c&H403F33&}Infirm{\alpha&HFF}ary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs54\b1\pos(841.5,421.5)\frx6\fry16\frz349.267\c&H403F33&}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru! Run suddenly fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the nurse has the day off. What are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. How about asking another teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was just deprived of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't got an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sunny this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a light shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we make it if we run?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tooru. Watch for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered this recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attract the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stay there. Come back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, now I'm wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Run-chan is in such a state right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I work at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.18,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\c&H594F4D&\fnEraserDust\fs72\pos(70.5,538.5)}Hand in the training camp \Nconsent form to your teacher {\c&H93837B&}or to Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, we have to dry you off quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you don't need an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this bad at my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect this from an elementary schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm. Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressing alike is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then one of us can{\fscx200}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nagi-chan! Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. I was wondering what you were up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, you're completely soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My house is nearby. Should we go dry your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think there's somebody here who attracts the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real downpour, but we could just run through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be as scary if all of us get drenched!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just to Nagi's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get soaked, so I'm calling a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual for a high schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'll stop if we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, let's get a tax{\fscx200}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan's place is this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People usually get the blues whenever it rains, but they are so cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's falling. It's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:47.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs54\c&H000000&\frz270\pos(1512,307.5)}Kitou-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\fs42\c&H000000&\frz270\pos(1420.5,307.5)}Hobby       Poem
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.02,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.48,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.24,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take a bath right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My brother is home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a brother, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I have friends over right now, so don't use the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, do you call your brother "Aniki" or "Onii-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call him "Aniki"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two people can fit in the bath at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to split into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll go first with Run then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get changed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I've never talked to Tooru alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything to say to break the silence? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put something on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bunch of DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The True Story of a Scary Urban Legend" or silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true dilemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, put your clothes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's jump in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Run, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, bangs sure can change how a person looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of getting that reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to get out soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We have to let Tooru and Yuuko-chan in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only the two of them in my room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think they'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get along great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess they do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! This is bad! And it's not getting any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! If I close my eyes, it's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I want to scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can now go and take a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yuuko, the bath is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.00,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, that was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally we're having a bath, right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's jump in then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, do you ever get scared when you have to close your eyes as you wash your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I couldn't stand shampoo at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shampoo got into my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the shower head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes, my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuuko! You're being too noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My senses are going numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, look, I can see an oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko. How was the water temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, turn off the heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could dry our clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel rejuvenated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me worry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the rain will stop soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is raining hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On rainy days, my hair kinda falls flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine puffs up, and I can't keep it together at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we have different hair types.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, let me touch your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah. Yuuko-chan, your hair is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.15,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no split ends at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.32,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These clothes are cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I'm doing something important here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to continue playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat Nagi's records.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nails are quite pretty, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing something to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels nice, but it's kinda awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tooru, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! {Run}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.78,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep still! {Nagi}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it's stopped yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is raining hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I like the sound of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I think I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, close your eyes and listen too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no. I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're right. It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow, it sounds like a grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting hungry already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you then. Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, thanks for the umbrellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that umbrella is really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still pouring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the next train coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you can use the bathroom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to be careful, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, sorry to have kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, at long last, Yutaka and Mipo-rin will be appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it, we've been at it for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, enough reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, weren't we supposed to appear in episode 1? {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did appear in the opening, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on A Channel, "Classmates."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.64,0:24:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, upperclassmen will also be appearing, as well as classmates.
